{"tid":339810,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣  對天外Online好深刻","createTime":"2017-07-29T11:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T06:06:16.000Z","uid":83063,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"efa410b46c91f7c8e5126b0e1e331d83c977b10f","tid":339810,"uid":83063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:14:48.000Z","msg":"可以話係第一隻玩既Online Game    果陣屋企岩岩有上網  就玩呢隻Game   小四左右   <br />\n玩過術士 藥師同 風水師 得術士上到60Lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他太難升  要靠隨任/重課谷裝打羅剎<br />\n<br />\n隻Game最特別系統就係英雄卡   <br />\n果陣時人唔夠英雄打係一件好正常既事  正因為咁先顯得出佢既重要性  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到一出左英雄石系統  其實成隻Game已經失去佢既特別   過左無耐就無玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c5a83bca9c6f2f59e004c8838a286c9d2eb359","tid":339810,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:16:41.000Z","msg":"個個人小學雞玩既第一隻online都深刻嫁啦"},{"pid":"39d99bc9af6127ae16b3f9f86ec3c0cce401e43c","tid":339810,"uid":17174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:25:12.000Z","msg":"英雄系統好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時日日都去種英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c3ead36d2d81040155a0ad29a416d55959689b","tid":339810,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:37:08.000Z","msg":"港ser執左 唔係既話 我諗到而家仲會時不時玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571ed1169ff740543120873bcc02e8f42fbc7756","tid":339810,"uid":84780,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:40:14.000Z","msg":"都係第1隻玩 港服免費ser 夜靈殿一份子 <br />\n唔玩之前 全ser頭幾名100lv藥師"},{"pid":"53a631fe67be353f41a7628dabc37abac86b5407","tid":339810,"uid":12802